Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.50,0:01:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.44,0:01:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.01,0:01:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.28,0:01:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為王子的置物箱一定能看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.41,0:01:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底想看什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漫畫裡不是常看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一打開置物箱 巧克力就霹靂啪拉地掉出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想在真實生活中應該不會發生那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.82,0:01:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.12,0:01:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是和布穀鳥幼鳥同樣的行為造成的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.56,0:01:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布穀鳥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像布穀鳥會把伯勞鳥的蛋從鳥巢推下去一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.03,0:01:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少女們為了讓你一眼看到她的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會把先放進來的巧克力給丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據就在那個垃圾桶裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.21,0:02:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 好過分哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想奪取最後一個巧克力的那隻老鷹就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.82,0:02:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 巧克力罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是由希的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是二月14日情人節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.51,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.01,0:02:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.14,0:02:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就展現出他的戰鬥心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要送給草摩同學的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.11,0:03:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力是要送給…草摩同學的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學…\N由希同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時下的女孩真是可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.78,0:03:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿會突然從街角衝過去似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.15,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於十二生肖的男孩們來說 或許這是最可怕的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.09,0:03:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是送給小魚和小花的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年都麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高興 妳想要什麼回禮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用什麼回禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老是在麻煩妳們 這個就算是謝禮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.77,0:03:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送你巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.84,0:03:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿夾好受歡迎喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.55,0:03:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生意不錯哦 連阿夾都這麼熱門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.35,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是情人節啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.32,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 家裡也很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 出去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要暫時消失一陣子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.29,0:04:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 我的最愛～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.86,0:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不想見樂羅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是情人節啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是情侶們重要的節日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰跟誰是情侶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.41,0:04:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 你別亂插嘴 不然家裡會被拆掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.41,0:04:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該早點出去旅行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到今天居然是情人節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.75,0:05:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都會知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳送他巧克力了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為阿夾太害羞了 一直都不肯收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情人節快樂 阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝滿了我今年對你的愛的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人哪會吃那種甜死人的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.37,0:05:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 原來阿夾討厭巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 最討厭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別講一大堆歪理了 我叫你吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你吃\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快吃\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快吃！\N不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.93,0:05:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳該不會也準備了巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.73,0:05:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是準備送給大家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該先問一下大家喜不喜歡吃巧克力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.31,0:05:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒很想…想吃小透的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這個送給紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你早就想要了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直受你們照顧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.26,0:06:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡…我哪有照顧妳什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我真的好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.40,0:06:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透愛的巧克力撫平了我身心的疲憊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.64,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌棄的話 樂羅也來一個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.98,0:06:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有啊 好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.82,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有波鳥、潑春、紅葉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.75,0:06:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好是能親手拿給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到妳準備得還真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.16,0:06:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為包裝得很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以忍不住就買了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.43,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我卻不知道他們喜不喜歡巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳別理會阿夾說的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.41,0:07:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些能大言不慚地說出"身為男人"這種話的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.31,0:07:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實根本是不了解真正的"男子氣概"的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.95,0:07:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨意踐踏"人的心"和"人的愛"的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.55,0:07:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說是當男人了 連當人的資格都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我不應該買巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而應該選像"拳頭仙貝"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是"雷餅"這類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比較有男子氣概的點心才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些也挺好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃就是了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾吃我的巧克力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.75,0:07:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了 我會再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 阿春告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和由希和好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.99,0:08:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還說只要你們更了解對方 感情搞不好會更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.73,0:08:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能這樣的話 我也會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.47,0:08:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.61,0:08:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小波 我送你的情人節巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我騙你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小透送你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.95,0:08:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人的份也都託我拿來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.96,0:09:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情人節就這樣子度過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了 大家把筆放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後一個月的時間過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉眼間期末考也結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然考試很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.61,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但考試結束時的解脫感是我最愛的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.72,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 我考得很好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我平常還答得多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.99,0:09:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳考得不錯啊 那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.23,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要肯努力 小透也一樣辦得到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為由希肯教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}只\N是\N來\N搗\N蛋\N的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他自己也要溫書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻還仔細解說 只為了讓我聽懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.84,0:09:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 妳太誇張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.71,0:09:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學…他笑得好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.52,0:09:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼 他們到底在講什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個電波女人太可怕 害我們無法靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.73,0:10:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花島同學 妳好像很會念書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.23,0:10:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有電波 感覺又很有知識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上學期的期末考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.87,0:10:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳平均考了幾分呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.34,0:10:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 那時候我每天接受輔導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父母都被找來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我媽媽還哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.32,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 妳電波的威力呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.15,0:10:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我笨的程度連電波也無法彌補
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.06,0:10:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 花島 還有人比妳更笨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.63,0:10:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妳不會是指我吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢話 當然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒接受過課後輔導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父母也沒被找來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾其實功課不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 什麼叫"其實"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不在乎輸贏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這跟那沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.52,0:11:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 其實你是那種每天孜孜不倦K著書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻唸錯考試範圍 自我爆炸型的笨蛋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼一猜就中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.16,0:11:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近他老關在房間裡 原來就是在念書啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.90,0:11:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到他勤奮念書的模樣就不禁叫人莞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.24,0:11:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過阿夾還是活蹦亂跳的模樣比較適合他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田 妳來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.56,0:11:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好打工的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.53,0:11:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.98,0:12:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒看到妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期末考考完了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天開始我會努力工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫了大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.54,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是剛來 快點進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.78,0:12:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼晚了 還這麼有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次來小紫家 好興奮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.59,0:12:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.82,0:12:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人的人又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.33,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 剛洗完澡很舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的好精神就是叫我不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:13:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾在欺負人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.57,0:13:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉 肚子餓不餓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這點叫我不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.61,0:13:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉 你說了今天來住這裡的原因了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.62,0:13:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有問題問小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.62,0:13:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是幾月幾日呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.16,0:13:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是…三月14日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三月14日是White day
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.77,0:13:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以明天我要回禮給妳 送妳溫泉旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.91,0:13:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅行的名稱就是"我和小透兩人的溫泉之旅"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用取名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的溫泉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是草摩家經營的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.65,0:13:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.75,0:13:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招待我去那種高級的場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.92,0:13:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說太奢侈了 我一定會遭天譴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 只不過是溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是要請妳去巴黎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕的話太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.60,0:14:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就趁這個機會消除一下家事和打工的疲勞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道小透妳不高興？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興 我好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.44,0:14:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希和阿夾也要一起去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.61,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這小鬼 怎麼擅自決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去嘛 一起去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別搞錯了 我是不會去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會去 難得有這機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就更不會去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.44,0:14:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢的問題你別擔心 我存了很多零用錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.27,0:14:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是錢的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.34,0:14:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 講到錢…小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.21,0:14:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳上個月的旅行基金還沒交啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.71,0:14:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接到妳班導師電話的爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.05,0:14:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打電話跟我說他要幫妳付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.92,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 不行 真的不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.46,0:15:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上個月因為很多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.23,0:15:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我這個月拿到薪水就會付清了 別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經告訴導師了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.81,0:15:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳上個月明明有打工 為什麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是拿去買情人節的巧克力了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 學期旅行要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.62,0:15:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…快去…洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩服佩服 你還真能忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力不可能憑空掉下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是小透自己掏腰包買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.11,0:16:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼都沒想到這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她老是傻笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會去注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管他什麼情理巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她這樣增加自己的困擾要幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛不拿那些錢去買自己的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是交旅行基金呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.96,0:16:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她將來一定會吃大虧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.36,0:16:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她人生的百分之七十一定會在吃虧中度過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.23,0:16:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 昨天我參加讀書會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.74,0:16:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在讀書會之前 有個小孩去買了本書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫做"世界的笨蛋故事全集"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小孩很喜歡奇怪的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前也買了本"濃湯的宇宙"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家一起看了那本書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.96,0:16:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中有一段是講"世界最笨的旅人"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨旅人外出去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底有多笨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.60,0:16:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個旅人常一下子就上當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請借我點藥錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被鎮上的人所騙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙走了他的錢、衣服和鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.11,0:17:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.18,0:17:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒錢買種子種田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個旅人因為笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到鎮上的人說"謝謝你幫助我"時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.96,0:17:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還感動地說"祝你幸福 祝你幸福"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.47,0:17:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於 旅人全身赤裸 他感到很羞恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以決定到森林裡去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.47,0:17:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果這次他又碰到住在森林的魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.21,0:17:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼因為想吃旅人的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就講了很多好話想騙他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.32,0:17:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然旅人再度被騙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.12,0:17:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先給了根腳 後來又給它一根手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.40,0:18:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後 旅人只剩下頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.24,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還是把眼睛給了最後那隻魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.64,0:18:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隻魔鬼一邊吃著他的眼睛一邊跟他說"謝謝"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.01,0:18:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並說"我有禮物要回送給你"把禮物放在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.15,0:18:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果竟是張寫了"笨蛋"的紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.19,0:18:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是旅人他卻哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 謝謝 這是我第一次收到的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.16,0:18:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興 我好高興 謝謝你 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從失去眼睛的地方不停地流下眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.81,0:18:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後旅人就這樣死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.82,0:18:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故事講完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.02,0:18:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友都很瞧不起旅人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我閉上了眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.93,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並想起了旅人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了一直被騙到最後只剩一個頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.14,0:19:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還邊說"謝謝"邊哭的旅人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候我突然感覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.75,0:19:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.62,0:19:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,損失、辛勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想這些都是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.69,0:19:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為旅人根本沒想到這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.10,0:19:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許對別人來說他很笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但對我來說他一點都不笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.21,0:19:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對某人來說他可能很好騙 但我絕不會騙他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.01,0:19:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的只是想讓她高興而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希呢？阿夾呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.82,0:20:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還是覺得她很笨嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛 你們想到什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 早安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也陪妳去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.32,0:20:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒準備回禮給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.26,0:20:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就忍受那個笨蛋由希陪妳一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.83,0:20:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦 就算沒有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可能也會玩得很高興…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.55,0:20:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能陪我去我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.68,0:21:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我好高興 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的拿妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾你一大早就好耀眼喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.77,0:21:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.71,0:21:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.88,0:21:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.01,0:21:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～～阿夾欺負人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.45,0:21:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾說要跟我們一起去溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.75,0:21:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.66,0:21:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.66,0:21:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這趟大家一起去的"信步溫泉之旅"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.67,0:21:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好期待
